algebras, {\em Comm. Math. Phys.} to appear.
\item Chapter 4: F. A. Bais, T. Tjin, P. van Driel, Covariantly coupled
chiral algebras, {\em Nucl. Phys.} {\bf B357} (1991) 632; J. de Boer and
